en to girls, especially in the United States, a choice possibly influenced by the female character so named in  Enid Bagnold's  novel National Velvet (  1935 ), which was made into a film (  1944 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Meredith ap Llewelyn was born about 1285, in Wales as the son of Maredudd ap Llewelyn and Mrs Maredudd ap Llewelyn. He had at least 2 daughters with Lleneu Verch Llewellyn."},"et":{"about 1285–":"umbes 1285–Surnud","1285–Male":"1285–Surnud","1290–Female":"1290–Surnud","1314–Female":"1314–Surnud","1345–1370":"1345–1370","1303–Male":"1303–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1314":"1314","1303":"1303","1345":"1345","1285":"1285","1370":"1370","about 1285":"umbes 1285","1290":"1290","Cardiganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Cardiganshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Wales":"Wales","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Wales"},"fi":{"about 1285–":"noin 1285–Kuollut","1285–Male":"1285–Kuollut","1290–Female":"1290–Kuollut","1314–Female":"1314–Kuollut","1345–1370":"1345–1370","1303–Male":"1303–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1314":"1314","1303":"1303","1345":"1345","1285":"1285","1370":"1370","about 1285":"noin 1285","1290":"1290","Cardiganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Cardiganshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Wales":"Wales","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Wales"},"fr":{"about 1285–":"environ 1285–Décédé","1285–Male":"1285–Décédé","1290–Female":"1290–Décédée","1314–Female":"1314–Décédée","1345–1370":"1345–1370","1303–Male":"1303–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1314":"1314","1303":"1303","1345":"1345","1285":"1285","1370":"1370","about 1285":"environ 1285","1290":"1290","Cardiganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Cardiganshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Wales":"Galles","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Galles","lifeSummary":"Meredith ap Llewelyn est né environ 1285, à Galles, fils de Maredudd ap Llewelyn et Mrs Maredudd ap Llewelyn. Il a eu au moins 2 filles avec Lleneu Verch Llewellyn."},"de":{"about 1285–":"um 1285–Verstorben","1285–Male":"128